name: Guelph Community Health Centre - Wyndham St N
comment:
Health centre focused on family and community health * health professionals assess and treat non-life-threatening injuries or illnesses * referrals to other local health services and personal development groups

Community-led health teams develop programs to improve the social supports and conditions that affect long-term health

Breastfeeding Support - Counselling for breastfeeding mothers * phone calls or home visits * breast pump rentals * discussion of the effects of foods and medications on breast milk

Clinical Dietitian - Nutritional information and education * one-on-one, couple, or family sessions for people with food and health-related concerns

Services and Programs:
  • Guelph - Downtown Location - Primary Care Services
  • Guelph - Stone Road Mall - EarlyON Child and Family Centre Guelph
  • Guelph Civic Museum - EarlyON Mobile Site
  • Indigenous Health and Wellness Program
  • Puslinch Community Centre - Aberfoyle EarlyON Mobile Site
  • Shelldale Satellite Clinic
